# New Realtime Event

## Arguments
- `name`: Event name (kebab-case, e.g., `order-placed`)
- `domain`: Domain context (e.g., `billing`, `auth`, `catalog`)
- `producer`: Service that publishes the event
- `consumers` (optional): Comma-separated services that consume the event

## Steps

### 1. Define Event Schema
- Create shared type in `packages/node/shared-types/src/events/{domain}.ts` (or add to existing):
```typescript
export interface {{ toPascalCase .name }}Event {
  // Define event payload fields
}
```
- Export from package barrel file

### 2. Create Kafka Topic
- Add KafkaTopic CR to `k8s/helm/{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}/infra/kafka/templates/`:
```yaml
apiVersion: kafka.strimzi.io/v1beta2
kind: KafkaTopic
metadata:
  name: {{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}.{domain}.{name}
  labels:
    strimzi.io/cluster: {{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}-kafka
spec:
  partitions: 3
  replicas: 1
  config:
    retention.ms: "604800000"  # 7 days
```

### 3. Add Producer Code
- In `apps/{producer}/src/events/`:
  - Create `publish-{name}.ts` with typed publish function
  - Use standard event envelope with correlationId
{{ if .Computed.HasDapr }}- Publish via Dapr: `daprClient.pubsub.publish('pubsub', topic, envelope)`{{ else }}- Publish via Kafka producer: `producer.send(topic, envelope)`{{ end }}

### 4. Add Consumer Code (for each consumer)
- In `apps/{consumer}/src/events/`:
  - Create `handle-{name}.ts` with typed handler
  - Ensure handler is **idempotent** (check for duplicate eventId)
{{ if .Computed.HasDapr }}- Register subscription in Helm values:
```yaml
dapr:
  subscriptions:
    - topic: {{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}.{domain}.{name}
      route: /events/{name}
```{{ else }}- Register consumer in service startup:
```typescript
consumer.subscribe('{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}.{domain}.{name}', handler);
```{{ end }}

### 5. Dead Letter Queue
- Add DLQ topic: `{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}.{domain}.{name}.dlq`
- Configure retry policy (3 retries, exponential backoff)
- Failed messages go to DLQ after retries exhausted

## Topic Naming
```
{{ .Project.Metadata.Name }}.<domain>.<event-name>
```

## Checklist
- [ ] Event schema defined in shared-types package
- [ ] Kafka topic CR created
- [ ] Producer publishes with standard envelope
- [ ] Consumer handles idempotently
- [ ] DLQ topic configured
- [ ] correlationId propagated for tracing
